{"tid":2515622,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"連登男神林作遭妻子裕美狂踩乸型度縮食軟飯不孝子弱智兼老套","createTime":"2021-05-04T06:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T06:53:48.000Z","uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7912ad8c77a84d17a3b1cf92370165ea272bbdf7","tid":2515622,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:18:43.000Z","msg":"裕美晚上在觀塘參與網上直播音樂會，已有一年多沒有表演機會，她說只會在沖涼時才有機會唱。她平時不願意跟男友林作合唱，批評林作說話聲線：<span class=\"red\">「佢講嘢好乸，撚狗時又扮cute，對住我講嘢又太乸，我講嘢仲ｍan過佢。佢唱歌又五音不全，好似細路仔吊高把聲，但又有時壓低聲唱，我經常投訴佢要ｍan啲。」</span>裕美喜歡較雄壯的男人，自爆有時在房未去到床上已很厭惡這男友。<br />\n<br />\n昨日林作參加拳賽，裕美表示他頸和手臂肌肉拉傷，但她不感「肉痛」：「對佢從來唔會，我有話介紹物理治療師畀佢，但佢想要自然好。」她曾笑言會打死林作，就算林作練拳後她也不怕被打倒，很權威地表示：<span class=\"red\">「佢試吓打我，我實打死佢，佢唔敢撩我，成日都話因為我養佢。」</span><br />\n<br />\n裕美越爆越多，自信地謂做生意賺的錢比林作的收入多幾倍，更會每月支付生活費給林作：<span class=\"red\">「自從我哋一齊之後，佢媽咪就冇養佢，所以通常出街都係我畀錢，我就好闊綽嘅，反而有時佢畀錢就計住，佢好度住啲錢。」</span>裕美謂每月找林作詢問簡單的法律資訊，以5位數字作酬勞，笑謂現當作是投資，期望將來有收穫從林作身上撈一大筆。她又爆林作母親很疏爽買很貴的名牌手袋，搭的士找續少2元卻會投訴，裕美指可能富有的人就會計較一點，但她則覺得對錢財計較不容易發達。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZnt9tMurMPFNtpTuBSewQTcFainZ5mj9949xEMUvqKJ9?filename=ETYabU9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FETYabU9.png&h=63d7c9fa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n裕美放褔利大曬42寸美腿引死記者<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210503/IJRDSS4JNRDGLJWKY3QASXXWUQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210503%2FIJRDSS4JNRDGLJWKY3QASXXWUQ%2F&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnrccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=ffde2454\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210503%2FIJRDSS4JNRDGLJWKY3QASXXWUQ%2F&h=01cf6bac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210503/IJRDSS4JNRDGLJWKY3QASXXWUQ/</a>"},{"pid":"8fc527b012a916221256113690835a83f2b04b36","tid":2515622,"uid":38539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:20:24.000Z","msg":"笑撚死，果然物以類聚、人以群分，連登仔力捧林作，咁係因為本性相近，都係屬於個啲廢柴型男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1bdc182d7f7e3959dec3a52d052da5794c1b336","tid":2515622,"uid":32227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:25:03.000Z","msg":"毒果做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd139c18c19f978a405c5bc901600d67b7e663e0","tid":2515622,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8474064ff16039b911ba604526991b05ff3ca510","tid":2515622,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:49:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3230e58f4f7b2999f6a14c3099a2532bbf680232","tid":2515622,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:53:15.000Z","msg":"丫媽爹 丫媽爹 塔錯車"},{"pid":"126dcbf66ae84fe6ef0a68a522981e6b179b8b79","tid":2515622,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:53:48.000Z","msg":"邊個話佢係連登男神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}